<li id="cite_note-Revision-15"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Revision_15-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Revision_15-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith1831" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Joseph_Smith" title="Joseph Smith">Smith, Joseph</a> (April 4, 1831). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.josephsmithpapers.org/paper-summary/old-testament-revision-2/31#full-transcript"><i>Old Testament Revision 2</i></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/The_Joseph_Smith_Papers" title="The Joseph Smith Papers">The Joseph Smith Papers</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Old+Testament+Revision+2&amp;rft.date=1831-04-04&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.josephsmithpapers.org%2Fpaper-summary%2Fold-testament-revision-2%2F31%23full-transcript&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACurses+of+Cain+and+Ham+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
